data.description: Unlimited possibilities on this 20+ acre piece of property.  Everything is done in this nearly new 3 bedroom 2 bath manufactured home, so spend your time outside creating your perfect country paradises.  With a sprawling field, large stating timber, and Little Ferris Creek Meandering through the property, there are plenty of opportunities to raise animals, plant a garden, and more than enough space to build the shop of your dreams.  Property is zoned RA5 so be sure to chat with the county regarding possible lot division.  Don't waste a single moment.  Come see this property today!
